+```python
+"""EvalAgentInvoker -- temporary facade hiding RC/GA call shape during migration.
+
+D-07 EXPLICIT JUSTIFICATION (per EVAL-INVENTORY.md round-15):
+
+1. Framework primitive considered: Agent.run(messages) direct.
